sais axess peoplesoft student affairs student affairs information services applications tools & technology support projects & plans policies & standards stanford university student affairs all stanford search submit axess peoplesoft axess peoplesoft student affairs information systems information stanford universal faculty perennial applications stanford university uses the peoplesoft student administration system provided by oracle to track and manage all student academic information courses enrollments grades instructors academic standing degree progress transcript information etc student financial information financial aid loans student bill etc student personal information official and preferred names emergency contact information email addresses phone numbers etc stanford curriculum and instruction offered on a term by term basis peoplesoft more popularly known around campus as axess is considered stanford's authoritative record for the information cited above axess itself is a term coined from the stanford axe which is of course the treasured symbol of the stanford cal rivalry and that fact that the system is used to access the information above stanford first introduced the campus to peoplesoft in 2000 2001 groups sais printer friendly version calendar student affairs the student affairs division is responsible for programs and services that focus on students and their stanford experience while also engaging with faculty staff parents alumni and the community at large copyright 2011 stanford university terms of use copyright complaints report a problem with this site
